        <updateDate>2007-09-14T19:41:57Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Surface Transportation and Taxation Equity Act or STATE Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to reduce the federal excise tax on gasoline and special fuels (but not below two cents per gallon) by corresponding increases in fuel taxes imposed by States after March 5, 2007.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Surface Transportation and Taxation Equity Act</title>
    <titles>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to reduce the Federal tax on fuels by the amount of any increase in the rate of tax on such fuel by the States.</title>
